#: ../../user-manual/administer/static-pages.rst:305
msgid ""
"The \"Slug\" :term:`field` is a page title referenced by AtoM code to manage"
" URLs; it **cannot be changed** for the :term:`Home page` or the "
":term:`About page`. However, it can be edited in any static pages that you "
